<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Macos on Tech In Sight</title><link>https://techinsight.pages.dev/categories/macos/</link><description>Recent content in Macos on Tech In Sight</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 10:49:20 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://techinsight.pages.dev/categories/macos/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>关掉iTerm一个非常恼人的功能</title><link>https://techinsight.pages.dev/p/%E5%85%B3%E6%8E%89iterm%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E9%9D%9E%E5%B8%B8%E6%81%BC%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD/</link><pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 10:49:20 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://techinsight.pages.dev/p/%E5%85%B3%E6%8E%89iterm%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E9%9D%9E%E5%B8%B8%E6%81%BC%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD/</guid><description>&lt;p>近期不知道是怎么回事，
iTerm鼠标点一下就会出现一个外框，再点一下就消失了，非常讨厌，猜测了多种可能的原因：ohmyzsh、power10k，换到最基础的bash配置还是存在，基本上就确定是iTerm的问题了，但找不到是哪里配置的这个，索性就用appcleaner卸载，把所有配置文件也都删了，然后用homebrew重新安装，结果一打开就发现了问题所在。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>不点击时这样&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://techinsight.pages.dev/p/%E5%85%B3%E6%8E%89iterm%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E9%9D%9E%E5%B8%B8%E6%81%BC%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD/no-click.png"
